        "Dear Management,",
        "I'm writing this letter in connection with my last stay at your hotel and the compensation your manager promised me to pay for my uncomfortable stay.",
        "I'm Akila and I stayed at your hotel room 206 on the 22nd of July 2022. I heard a terrible noise early in the morning from your central heating system which made it difficult for me to sleep. In addition, I had a terrible headache throughout the day due to this incident.",
